FWeaHy8A&oe=66E2C658"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Burj Alluqluq", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Dive into a virtual exploration of one of Jerusalem's most significant historical landmarks with the \"Burj Al-Luqluq VR\" app. This immersive virtual reality experience transports you directly into the heart of Burj Al-Luqluq, allowing you to wander through its ancient architecture and uncover the layers of history that have shaped this iconic site. Through a carefully curated interactive tour, users can engage with the rich cultural and historical narratives of Burj Al-Luqluq, learning about its significance in Jerusalem's storied past.\n\nThe app features detailed reconstructions of the site, enriched with historical facts and stories that bring the past to life. Whether you're a history enthusiast, a cultural explorer, or simply looking for a unique virtual reality experience, \"Burj Al-Luqluq VR\" offers a captivating journey through time. Experience the beauty of Jerusalem's heritage from a new perspective, exploring the intricacies of Burj Al-Luqluq's architecture and the historical events that have unfolded within its walls.", "short_description": "Discover the depths of history and culture at Burj Al-Luqluq with our unique virtual reality app. \"Burj Al-Luqluq VR\" offers an interactive tour that takes you on a historical journey inside one of Jerusalem's most prominent landmarks, providing an immersive opportunity to explore its rich heritage and ancient stories."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/burj-alluqluq-vr", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Mohammad Salah", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.burjalluqluq.org/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "726368587961803"}]